channel.title: Problem with starting [525] HD server
channel.description:
Iam trying to login into my 525 HD server. Iam using the files posted by Pur3zscape http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?topic=413135.0
I run the source and it works just fine, but (setting up world) keeps on loading and it won't load.. [URL=http://img19.imageshack.us/i/20100705021118.png/][IMG]http://img19.imageshack.us/img19/622/20100705021118.th.png[/img][/URL]
Uploaded with [URL=http://imageshack.us]ImageShack.us[/URL]
And when running the client it just stops at some point to load world list or something..
[URL=http://img808.imageshack.us/i/20100705021034.png/][IMG]http://img808.imageshack.us/img808/443/20100705021034.th.png[/img][/URL]

Sometimes the client run and when i try to login it says error connecting please try another world and there is'nt any world in the world list. can someone find a solution for it please? Thanks~
